Text: There is 16 episods in season 7, not 14 ... (according to wikipedia)

Wikipedia can be written by anyone and I go by IMDB which states season 7 is 14 episodes and so does USA. I was watching it the night of when they stated that it was the final episode of this season. So, this is the complete season. Thanks.
It's 16, but the final 2 episodes are musical specials that are not being aired until December.
Which in turn is a 2 hr Christmas special and still not accounted for in this season which is why episode 14 states that it is the season finale.
